dct_description_sm: Map shows the city of Moukden (Mukden, Shenyang) at centre right. It depicts parts of Manchuria and northern Korea.
dessiné, héliogravé et publié par le Service géographique de l'Armée (Avril 1899).
Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Longitudes on map shown as 120°--126°, "méridien de Paris."
Stamped at lower right corner of map margin: Majoration 50%.
